Date: 1994-07-18

Title: ``Integrating in'' and exact superpotentials in 4d

Authors: Ken Intriligator

Comments: 10 pages, RU-94-57

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B336 (1994) 409-414

We discuss integrating out matter fields and integrating in matter fields infour dimensional supersymmetric gauge theories. Highly nontrivial exactsuperpotentials can be easily obtained by starting from a known theory andintegrating in matter.